## Relay-D2 HandoffDocument Generation
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 已实现
**模块：** `crates/auto-forge/src/relay/handoff.rs`
**标签：** stack:backend
**依赖：** Relay-G2, AgentConfig-D1

```rust
pub struct HandoffDocument {
    pub from: String,
    pub to: String,
    pub run_id: String,
    pub checkpoint_id: u64,
    pub summary: String,
    pub decisions: Vec<Decision>,
    pub open_questions: Vec<Question>,
    pub spec_updates: Vec<SpecUpdate>,
    pub work_product: Vec<WorkProduct>,
    pub context_for_next: ContextPointers,
    pub token_usage: TokenUsage,
}

impl HandoffDocument {
    /// 根据智能体轮次历史和当前状态生成。
    pub fn generate(
        agent: &AgentInstance,
        turn_history: &[TurnRecord],
        specs: &SpecsDocument,
    ) -> Result<Self, HandoffError>;

    /// 渲染为 Markdown，供下一个智能体消费。
    pub fn render(&self) -> String;

    /// 使用低成本模型或规则将原始轮次历史压缩为摘要。
    pub async fn compress_history(
        history: &[TurnRecord],
        model: &ModelConfig,
    ) -> Result<String, CompressionError>;
}

pub struct ContextPointers {
    pub files_to_read: Vec<String>,
    pub specs_to_follow: Vec<String>,
    pub warnings: Vec<String>,
}

pub struct TokenUsage {
    pub step_input: u64,
    pub step_output: u64,
    pub cumulative: u64,
    pub budget_remaining: u64,
}
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Collecting: Agent turn complete
    Collecting --> Summarizing: Raw history gathered
    Summarizing --> Structured: Decisions extracted
    Structured --> Validated: Open questions identified
    Validated --> Rendered: Work product catalogued
    Rendered --> [*]
```

| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |
|---|---|---|
| `summary` | `String` | ≤200 词的执行摘要 |
| `decisions.id` | `String` | 决策标识符 |
| `decisions.status` | `String` | made / deferred / rejected |
| `open_questions.id` | `String` | 问题标识符 |
| `spec_updates.section_id` | `String` | 被修改的规范章节 |
| `work_product.path` | `String` | 文件路径或产物位置 |
| `work_product.lines` | `u32` | 上下文大小指示器 |

```
fn generate(agent, turn_history, specs):
    // Phase 1: Summarize (cheap model or rules)
    summary = compress_history(turn_history, cheap_model)
    
    // Phase 2: Extract decisions from agent's explicit handoff tool calls
    decisions = extract_decisions(turn_history)
    
    // Phase 3: Identify open questions from handoff tool calls
    questions = extract_open_questions(turn_history)
    
    // Phase 4: Catalog spec changes made by agent
    spec_updates = diff_specs(original_specs, current_specs)
    
    // Phase 5: List files touched
    work_product = agent.context.files_touched
    
    // Phase 6: Build context pointers for next agent
    pointers = build_context_pointers(agent.profession, next_profession, specs)
    
    return HandoffDocument { ... }
```


