## Relay-D11 Spawn Relay Tool & Background Driver
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 已实现
**模块：** `backend/src/forge/tools.rs`, `backend/src/relay/driver.rs`, `backend/src/forge/mod.rs`
**标签：** stack:backend
**依赖：** Relay-G13, Relay-A4, Relay-D1, Chat-D3, Errand-D1

### SpawnRelayTool

```rust
pub struct SpawnRelayTool;

impl Tool for SpawnRelayTool {
    fn name(&self) -> &'static str { "spawn_relay" }

    fn description(&self) -> &'static str {
        "Spawn an autonomous background relay pipeline. \
         Use this after you have completed discovery and written goals \
         to hand off execution to a serial pipeline of profession agents."
    }

    fn input_schema(&self) -> Value {
        json!({
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["flow_id", "task"],
            "properties": {
                "flow_id": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "enum": ["standard", "post_discovery", "fast_track", "bug_fix"]
                },
                "task": { "type": "string" },
                "mode": { "type": "string", "enum": ["gsd", "check"], "default": "gsd" },
                "context": { "type": "string" }
            }
        })
    }

    fn execute(&self, args: Value) -> Result<String, ToolError> {
        // 1. 验证 flow_id 和 mode
        // 2. 验证调用者职业是否拥有 spawn_relay 权限
        // 3. 生成 run_id = format!("run-{}", Uuid::new_v4())
        // 4. 返回包含 relay_spawned、run_id、flow_id、monitor_url 的 JSON
    }
}
```

### 职业白名单

| 职业 | `spawn_relay` 在 allowed_tools 中 | 典型用例 |
|---|---|---|
| assistant | ✅ | 接收完成 → 生成标准 Flow |
| advisor | ✅ | **发现完成 → 生成 post_discovery Flow** |
| architect | ✅ | 设计完成 → 从 planner 步骤生成 |
| planner | ❌ | — |
| tester | ❌ | — |
| coder | ❌ | — |
| reviewer | ❌ | — |
| documenter | ❌ | — |

### Forge Stream Handler Interception

```rust
// 在 forge_stream ReAct 循环中，工具执行后：
if name == "spawn_relay" {
    if let Ok(data) = serde_json::from_str::<Value>(&result_str) {
        if data.get("relay_spawned").and_then(|v| v.as_bool()) == Some(true) {
            // 1. 根据 flow_id 构建 FlowSpec
            let flow = match flow_id.as_str() {
                "standard" => standard_spec_flow(),
                "post_discovery" => post_discovery_flow(),
                // ...
            };

            // 2. 在 RunStore 中启动运行
            start_run(run_store, flow, &run_id);
            set_mode_on_engine(mode);

            // 3. 生成后台驱动
            tokio::spawn(relay::driver::drive_run(
                run_id.clone(),
                run_store.clone(),
                event_sender(),
                provider.clone(),
                task,
                project_path,
            ));

            // 4. 向聊天发送 RelaySpawned SSE
            event_tx.send(ForgeStreamEvent::RelaySpawned { ... });

            // 5. 将结果替换为友好消息
            result_str = "Relay pipeline started: {run_id}...";
        }
    }
}
```

### RelayDriver

```rust
pub async fn drive_run(
    run_id: String,
    run_store: RunStore,
    event_tx: broadcast::Sender<RunEventBroadcast>,
    provider: ClaudeProviderState,
    initial_task: String,
    project_path: String,
) {
    set_tool_context(&project_path, &run_id);

    loop {
        match advance_run(&run_store, &run_id) {
            Some(ExecuteStep { step_id, profession_id, .. }) => {
                // 从 RelayRegistry 默认配置构建智能体
                let agent = build_agent(&profession_id);

                // 构建消息：任务 + 前一次交接 + 关卡反馈
                let messages = build_step_messages(...);

                // 运行 AgentTurn
                let mut turn = AgentTurn::new(agent, ToolRegistry::new(), messages);
                turn.max_turns = turn.agent.profession.max_turns;
                let result = turn.run(&*provider, event_drain_tx).await;

                // 构建并提交交接
                let handoff = turn.to_handoff(&result, "next", &run_id, 0);
                let next = submit_handoff(&run_store, &run_id, handoff);

                // 处理下一个结果...
            }
            Some(WaitForHuman { .. }) => {
                wait_for_gate_resolution(&run_store, &run_id, &event_tx).await;
            }
            Some(Completed) | Some(Failed { .. }) | None => break,
        }
    }
}
```

### 步骤消息构建

```
## Task

{initial_task}

## Previous Agent's Handoff

{previous_handoff.render()}

## Feedback from Previous Attempt

- {gate_feedback[0]}
- {gate_feedback[1]}

You are step '{step_id}' ({profession_id}) in a relay pipeline.
Do your work using available tools. When finished, stop making tool calls.
```

