## Accessibility

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| Screen reader | `role="progressbar"` with `aria-valuenow`, `aria-valuemax`, `aria-label` |
| Tooltip accessible | `role="tooltip"` on hover popover |
| Color contrast | All palette colors meet WCAG AA on background |
| Keyboard | Focus on bar shows tooltip (`focusin`/`focusout` mirror `mouseenter`/`mouseleave`) |
| No color-only info | Each segment has profession label in tooltip, not just color |

---

## Animation

| Transition | Duration | Easing |
|---|---|---|
| Segment width change | 300ms | ease-out |
| Tooltip fade in | 150ms | ease |
| Tooltip fade out | 100ms | ease |
| Budget warning glow | instant on class change | — |
